Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:31.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在这儿\N{\fs40}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:44.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海蛇快要死了 对不对？\N{\fs40}The Sea Snake is going to die, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 小路 - 我当不了潮汛之主\N{\fs40}-Luke-- -I can't be Lord of the Tides.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,祖父是有史以来最伟大的航海家\N{\fs40}Grandsire was the greatest sailor who ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可我呢 船还没离港就会晕船\N{\fs40}I get greensick before the ship even leaves the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:58.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会搞砸所有事\N{\fs40}I'll just ruin everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:00.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也不想要潮头岛\N{\fs40}I don't want Driftmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:03.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,本该由魏蒙德爵士继承\N{\fs40}It should've passed on to Ser Vaemond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小路 我们无法选择自己的命运 是命运选择了我们\N{\fs40}We don't choose our destiny, Luke. It chooses us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:09.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但外公曾让您选择是否要继承王位\N{\fs40}Grandsire let you choose whether you'd be his heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您是这样告诉我们的\N{\fs40}You told us so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:20.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你想知道真实的情况吗？\N{\fs40}And do you want to know the truth of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:23.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我当时吓坏了\N{\fs40}I was frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当年我才十四岁\N{\fs40}I was four-and-ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和你现在一样大\N{\fs40}Same as you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:35.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我并未做好准备 成为七大王国的女王\N{\fs40}I wasn't ready to be Queen of the Seven Kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:38.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但这是我的职责所在\N{\fs40}But it was my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:41.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很快地 我就明白了\N{\fs40}And, in time, I came to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我得靠自己赢得继承权\N{\fs40}I had to earn my inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我和您不一样\N{\fs40}I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哪些方面 好孩子？\N{\fs40}In what way, sweet boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:49.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不像您那么...\N{\fs40}I'm not so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,完美\N{\fs40}perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我绝不完美\N{\fs40}I am anything but.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:10.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我父亲照顾我 帮助我做好继承的准备\N{\fs40}My father looked after me and helped to prepare me for my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的母亲也会为你做同样的事情\N{\fs40}Your mother will do the same for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,早上好 公主殿下\N{\fs40}Good morrow, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:17.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,早上好 洛伦特爵士\N{\fs40}Good morrow, Ser Lorent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝公主刚刚骑龙抵达\N{\fs40}Princess Rhaenys has just arrived on dragonback.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:25.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她请求立即与您和戴蒙王子见面\N{\fs40}She urgently requests an audience with you and Prince Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝·坦格利安公主到\N{\fs40}The Princess Rhaenys Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 洛伦特爵士\N{\fs40}Thank you, Ser Lorent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝公主\N{\fs40}Princess Rhaenys,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:55.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许您带来了科利斯伯爵康复的消息？\N{\fs40}might we hope for news of Lord Corlys's recovery?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯死了\N{\fs40}Viserys is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:05.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我与你同感悲痛 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}I grieve this loss with you, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:08.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的堂弟 你的父亲\N{\fs40}My cousin, your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他有颗善良的心\N{\fs40}possessed a kind heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有别的坏消息\N{\fs40}There is more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:29.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿已继位 加冕为王\N{\fs40}Aegon has been crowned as his successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们给伊耿加冕了？\N{\fs40}They crowned him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯怎么死的？\N{\fs40}How did Viserys die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个我不知道\N{\fs40}I could not say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:44.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,多久前的事？\N{\fs40}How long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:45.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一天前 顶多两天\N{\fs40}A day past, perhaps two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当王后密谋一切时 我被软禁在房间里\N{\fs40}I was made a prisoner in my quarters while the Queen made her preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯是被他们害死的\N{\fs40}Viserys has been slain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:56.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森要求你支持伊耿\N{\fs40}Alicent demanded you declare for Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs40}She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:02.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我拒绝了她\N{\fs40}I refused her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而你还活着\N{\fs40}And yet you are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:11.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,总主教在龙穴为伊耿加冕\N{\fs40}The High Septon crowned Aegon in the Dragonpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我亲眼目睹了仪式 之后骑上梅丽亚斯离开了\N{\fs40}I witnessed it myself just before I fled on Meleys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们当着民众的面拥他为王\N{\fs40}They crowned him before the masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:20.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因此民众把他视作合法的国王\N{\fs40}So that the masses would see him as their rightful king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:23.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后那贱人谋害了我哥哥 还篡夺了王位\N{\fs40}That whore of a Queen murdered my brother and stole his throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:24.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你本可以把他们全烧死\N{\fs40}And you could have burned them all for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:29.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 他们的叛国行径很可能引发战争\N{\fs40}A war is like to be fought over this treachery, to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:36.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但这场战争不会由我挑起\N{\fs40}But that war is not mine to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是赶来警告你们\N{\fs40}I only rushed this warning to you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为我忠于我的丈夫和我的家族\N{\fs40}out of loyalty to my husband and to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,绿党冲着你来了 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}The Greens are coming for you, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:48.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有你的孩子们\N{\fs40}And for your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:51.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们应该马上离开龙石岛\N{\fs40}You should leave Dragonstone at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,孩子要出生了\N{\fs40}The babe is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还没足月 预产期还远\N{\fs40}Her term is far from complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不该现在生的\N{\fs40}This should not be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,操 已经在生了\N{\fs40}It is fucking happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请冷静 公主殿下 来吧\N{\fs40}Keep your head about you, Princess. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们生过五次了\N{\fs40}We've done this five times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请您打起精神来 这次也会一样的\N{\fs40}Keep your spirit, and the sixth will be no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,走开 走开 走开 都走开\N{\fs40}Get off, get off, get off, get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,啊 啊 啊\N{\fs40}Ow, ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,派人沿着龙石岛周边巡逻\N{\fs40}I want patrols along the island's perimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:50.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,留意任何意图靠岸的小船\N{\fs40}looking for any small ships that might set ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果绿党现在发动进攻 必然是一场偷袭……\N{\fs40}If the Greens attack now, it will be by stealth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:55.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,绝非大张旗鼓\N{\fs40}not directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在我们人手不足 无法覆盖全岛\N{\fs40}We don't have enough men to surround the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但至少可以造大声势\N{\fs40}but we can make ourselves appear stronger than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:06.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,征召龙卫 他们是强有力的战士\N{\fs40}Conscript the Dragonkeepers. They're capable fighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别浪费时间\N{\fs40}Waste no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,马上去办 王子殿下\N{\fs40}It will be done, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这 算 什么？\N{\fs40}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs40}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:28.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不必对他太严格 王子殿下\N{\fs40}You might go easier on him, my Prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那样他才能学会您想教的\N{\fs40}so he can learn what you're trying to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:33.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们的母亲想要见你们\N{\fs40}Your lady mother needs to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,两位都去\N{\fs40}Both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,母亲？\N{\fs40}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,操\N{\fs40}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主殿下\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们的外公 韦赛里斯国王 已经去世了\N{\fs40}Your grandsire, King Viserys, has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯？\N{\fs40}Viserys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,绿党不承认继承顺位\N{\fs40}The Greens have repudiated the succession
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,占据了铁王座\N{\fs40}and claimed the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿已经称王了\N{\fs40}Aegon has been crowned king.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:16.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们要做什么？\N{\fs40}What is to be done about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在还不用\N{\fs40}Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:19.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙在哪儿？\N{\fs40}And where is Daemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs40}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他气得发狂\N{\fs40}Gone to madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在谋划战争\N{\fs40}Gone to plot his war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我去找戴蒙\N{\fs40}Leave Daemon with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:30.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰\N{\fs40}Jace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰卡里斯\N{\fs40}Jacaerys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:41.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不管我还拥有什么 你都是我的继承人了\N{\fs40}Whatever claim remains to me, you are now its heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:44.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没有我的命令 不要轻举妄动\N{\fs40}Naught is to be done but by my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:00.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今早有渡鸦来报\N{\fs40}A raven flew in this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:04.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海蛇已经退烧 并离开了暮临厅\N{\fs40}The Sea Snake's fever has broken, and he has left Evenfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他驶去哪了？\N{\fs40}Where is he sailing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就不清楚了 殿下\N{\fs40}That much is unclear, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:09.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们要向最近的盟友送出渡鸦：\N{\fs40}We'll send ravens to our nearest allies:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:12.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,达克林大人 马赛大人……\N{\fs40}Lords Darklyn, Massey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:14.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有巴尔艾蒙\N{\fs40}and Bar Emmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.49,Note_top,,0,0,0,,戴蒙！\N{\fs40}Daemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要跟学士谈一下吗 王子？\N{\fs40}Do you want to speak to the maester, my Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:30.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会亲自飞去河间地 确保徒利大人的支持\N{\fs40}I'll fly to the Riverlands myself and affirm Lord Tully's support.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不能这么做\N{\fs40}You will do no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:37.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我母亲下令 在其卧床期间 不许采取行动\N{\fs40}My mother has decreed no action be taken while she's abed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:47.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你来的正好 小王子\N{\fs40}It's good you're here, young Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,需要你骑上沃马克斯 巡逻空域\N{\fs40}You're needed to patrol the skies on Vermax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没听到我说的话？\N{\fs40}Did you hear what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,渡鸦 巴提摩斯大人\N{\fs40}The ravens, Lord Bartimos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,马上督办\N{\fs40}I shall see it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,传唤史蒂芬爵士\N{\fs40}Summon Ser Steffon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:04.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御林铁卫跟我去一趟龙山\N{\fs40}Our Kingsguard are needed on the Dragonmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,跟我来 我给你看看忠诚真正的意义\N{\fs40}Come with me. I'll show you the true meaning of loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们作为御林铁卫曾宣过誓\N{\fs40}You swore an oath as knights of the Kingsguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所有白骑士都是如此 王子\N{\fs40}As do all who wear the white cloak, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:23.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对谁？\N{\fs40}To whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:28.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我先是对杰赫里斯国王宣誓 王子\N{\fs40}I swore first to King Jaehaerys, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:32.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然后是对继位的韦赛里斯国王陛下\N{\fs40}And then to His Grace, King Viserys, when he succeeded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们认可真正的继承顺位吗\N{\fs40}Do you acknowledge the true line of succession?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,-认可 -认可 殿下\N{\fs40}-Yes. -Yes, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你们还记得\N{\fs40}Do you recall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:49.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯国王驾崩前指定谁为他的继承人吗？\N{\fs40}who King Viserys named as his heir before his death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉公主\N{\fs40}Princess Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:00.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我感谢你们对朝廷多年的效力\N{\fs40}I'm grateful for your long service to the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以我赐予你们一个选择\N{\fs40}So I'm presenting you with a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:30.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,重新宣誓效忠 对雷妮拉女王\N{\fs40}Swear anew your oath to Rhaenyra as your queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:35.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,及铁王座继承人杰卡里斯王子\N{\fs40}to Prince Jacaerys as the heir to the Iron Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或者……\N{\fs40}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:43.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你们支持篡位者 那现在就明说……\N{\fs40}if you support the usurper, speak it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不但能死得痛快 还能不失荣誉\N{\fs40}and you will have a clean and honorable death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:51.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但如果你们若选择背信弃义\N{\fs40}But if you choose treachery,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在假意宣誓 以后再行叛变\N{\fs40}if you swear fealty now only to later turn your cloaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:01.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,必将惨叫而死\N{\fs40}know that you will die...screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 让我们帮帮你吧\N{\fs40}Princess, let us help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:19.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 出去！ - 公主 求您了\N{\fs40}- Get out! - Princess, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 出去 - 您没必要自己受罪 公主\N{\fs40}- Get out. - You should not do this alone, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:22.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们帮忙吧\N{\fs40}Let us help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没有敌意 兄弟们\N{\fs40}I mean no harm, brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我对女王庄严起誓\N{\fs40}I swear to ward the Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:18.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我将尽心竭力守护她\N{\fs40}with all my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:22.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,付出生命在所不惜\N{\fs40}and give my blood for hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我将不娶妻……\N{\fs40}I shall take no wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不封地……\N{\fs40}hold no lands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不生子\N{\fs40}father no children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我将守护她的秘密\N{\fs40}I shall guard her secrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,服从她的命令……\N{\fs40}obey her commands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:46.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,追随她鞍前马后 维护她的名声和荣誉\N{\fs40}ride at her side, and defend her name and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,女王陛下\N{\fs40}My Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:59.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉·坦格利安一世\N{\fs40}Queen Rhaenyra Targaryen, First of Her Name,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,安达尔人 洛伊拿人和先民的女王\N{\fs40}Queen of the Andals and the Rhoynar and the First Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:07.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七国统治者暨全境守护者 驾到\N{\fs40}Lady of the Seven Kingdoms and Protector of the Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:12.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,酒 陛下\N{\fs40}Wine, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 雷妮亚\N{\fs40}Thank you, Rhaena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:29.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs40}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:56.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我们情况如何？- 我们有三十名骑士\N{\fs40}-What is our standing? -We have 30 knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一百名十字弓手 三百名士兵\N{\fs40}a hundred crossbowmen, and 300 men-at-arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:02.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,防守龙石岛是足够了 但要凭此征讨四方\N{\fs40}Dragonstone is relatively easy to defend, but as an instrument of conquest,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:04.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们还需要更多军队\N{\fs40}our army leaves a lot to be desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:06.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经传话给都城守备队中忠于我的人\N{\fs40}We have sent word to my loyal men in the City Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:09.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会得到一些支持 但不确定有多少\N{\fs40}I'll have some support there, but I cannot speak to the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:12.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公开宣誓我们的家族有赛提加 斯汤顿\N{\fs40}We already have declarations from Celtigar and Staunton,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:15.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,马赛 达克林和巴尔艾蒙\N{\fs40}Massey, Darklyn, Bar Emmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我母后出自艾林家\N{\fs40}My lady mother was an Arryn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谷地不会反叛血亲\N{\fs40}The Vale will not turn cloak against their own kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:26.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,奔流城公爵向来是您父亲的密友 陛下\N{\fs40}Riverrun was always a close friend to your father, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,经戴蒙王子准许\N{\fs40}With Prince Daemon's acquiescence,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:30.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经派渡鸦给葛拉佛大人送信\N{\fs40}I've already sent ravens to Lord Grover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:36.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,葛拉佛大人反复无常 容易动摇\N{\fs40}Lord Grover is fickle and easily swayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们需要用实力说服他\N{\fs40}He will need to be convinced of the strength of our position
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:41.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并确保一旦开战 我们会支援他\N{\fs40}and that we will support him should it come to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:43.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会亲自与他交涉\N{\fs40}I'm going to treat with him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那风息堡和临冬城呢？\N{\fs40}What of Storm's End and Winterfell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:48.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,史塔克家的人从不忘记誓言\N{\fs40}There has never lived a Stark who forgot an oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:51.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只要有了史塔克的支持 全北境就会追随\N{\fs40}And with House Stark, the North will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:54.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,需要提醒博洛斯·拜拉席恩大人 他父亲立过誓\N{\fs40}Lord Borros Baratheon will need to be reminded of his father's promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:09.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潮头岛有什么消息？\N{\fs40}What news from Driftmark?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:14.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯大人正航向龙石岛\N{\fs40}Lord Corlys sails for Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:17.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来向他的女王宣誓效忠\N{\fs40}To declare for his Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:21.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列里安家族舰队在我丈夫轭下\N{\fs40}The Velaryon fleet is in my husband's yoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:23.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他会决定航向\N{\fs40}He decides where they sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:26.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们会祈祷你和你丈夫的支持\N{\fs40}We shall pray for both you and your husband's support.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:29.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像我们每夜祈祷海蛇的康复\N{\fs40}Just as we prayed nightly for the Sea Snake's return to good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:33.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,狭海沿岸没有哪个港口\N{\fs40}There's no port on the Narrow Sea would dare to make
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:35.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,敢与瓦列利安舰队为敌\N{\fs40}an enemy of the Velaryon fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:38.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那我们的敌人呢？\N{\fs40}And our enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:39.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼斯特家族里找不到朋友\N{\fs40}We have no friends among the Lannisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:43.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,泰兰效力于国王之手已久 不可能掉转矛头\N{\fs40}Tyland has served the Hand too long to turn against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:45.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,奥托·海塔尔也需要兰尼斯特的舰队\N{\fs40}And Otto Hightower needs the Lannister fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没有兰尼斯特家族 我们在金牙城以西\N{\fs40}Without the Lannisters, we are not like to find
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:49.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不太可能找到盟友\N{\fs40}any allies west of the Golden Tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:50.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,河间地是关键 陛下\N{\fs40}The Riverlands are essential, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:23:00.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 陛下 只数人头是无意义的\N{\fs40}Pray forgive my bluntness, Your Grace, but talk of men is moot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.75,0:23:04.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您拥有自古瓦雷利亚毁灭以来\N{\fs40}Your cause owns a power that has not been seen in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:06.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,世所罕见的强大力量\N{\fs40}since the days of Old Valyria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:08.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙\N{\fs40}Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:12.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,绿党也有龙\N{\fs40}The Greens have dragons as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:14.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我数过 他们有三条成年龙\N{\fs40}They have three adults, by my count.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:17.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我们有叙拉克斯 科拉克休 和梅丽亚斯\N{\fs40}We have Syrax, Caraxes, and Meleys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:20.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的儿子们有沃马克斯 阿拉克斯和泰雷克休\N{\fs40}Your sons have Vermax, Arrax, and Tyraxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:22.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,贝妮拉有月舞\N{\fs40}Baela has Moondancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:24.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙 我们的龙没上过战场\N{\fs40}Daemon, none of our dragons have been to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:26.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有无主的龙\N{\fs40}There are also unclaimed dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海烟仍然栖息在潮头岛\N{\fs40}Seasmoke still resides on Driftmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:31.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,沃米索尔和银翼住在龙山\N{\fs40}Vermithor and Silverwing dwell on the Dragonmont,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:33.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,依然无人驯服\N{\fs40}still riderless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:36.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有三只野龙在这里筑巢\N{\fs40}Then there are the three wild dragons, all of whom nest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:37.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那么谁来做骑手？\N{\fs40}And who is to ride them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:41.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙石岛有十三条龙 他们只有四条\N{\fs40}Dragonstone has 13 to their 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:44.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我还有二十颗龙蛋 正在龙山孵化\N{\fs40}I also have a score of eggs incubating in the Dragonmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:48.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在……我们需要一个据点\N{\fs40}Now... we need a place to gather,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:51.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个足够大的立足点 来集结大军\N{\fs40}a toehold large enough to house a sizable host.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.85,0:23:53.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这里 赫伦堡\N{\fs40}Here, at Harrenhal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:55.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们切断西路 让龙包围君临\N{\fs40}We cut off the west, surround King's Landing with the dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.56,0:23:57.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,便可以在下个月前\N{\fs40}And we could have every Green head mounted on spikes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:23:59.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把绿党的脑袋统统插到枪尖上\N{\fs40}before the fucking moon turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:00.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:02.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们在岸边发现船只\N{\fs40}a ship has been sighted offshore:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:05.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一艘独行的帆船 挂着三头绿龙旗\N{\fs40}a lone galleon, flying a banner of a three-headed green dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,通知瞭望塔 警戒天空\N{\fs40}Alert the watchtowers. Sight the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.44,0:24:48.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我奉七国的统治者与守护者\N{\fs40}I come at the behest of the Dowager Queen Alicent,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.49,0:24:50.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王伊耿二世之母后\N{\fs40}mother of King Aegon, Second of His Name,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.74,0:24:53.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森王太后之命前来\N{\fs40}Lord and Protector of the Seven Kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.37,0:24:58.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,太后命我仅将此信息传达给雷妮拉公主本人\N{\fs40}I've been directed to deliver her message only to Princess Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.71,0:25:01.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主在哪？\N{\fs40}Where is the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:58.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉公主\N{\fs40}Princess Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.97,0:26:00.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我现在是雷妮拉女王了\N{\fs40}I'm Queen Rhaenyra now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.94,0:26:04.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尔等都是王国的叛徒\N{\fs40}And you all are traitors to the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.69,0:26:08.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿·坦格利安二世国王陛下\N{\fs40}King Aegon Targaryen, Second of His Name...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.19,0:26:13.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怀着仁慈和对和平的渴望\N{\fs40}in his wisdom and desire for peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.74,0:26:15.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,提出和谈条件\N{\fs40}is offering terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.62,0:26:19.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,承认伊耿为王\N{\fs40}Acknowledge Aegon as king
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.41,0:26:22.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在铁王座前向国王宣誓效忠\N{\fs40}and swear obeisance before the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.33,0:26:26.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为交换 陛下将承认你对龙石岛的所有权\N{\fs40}In exchange, His Grace will confirm your possession of Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.88,0:26:30.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在你死后 龙石岛将传予你的嫡子 杰卡里斯\N{\fs40}It will pass to your trueborn son, Jacaerys, upon your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.59,0:26:33.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,路斯里斯将被确认为潮头岛和\N{\fs40}Lucerys will be confirmed as the legitimate heir to Driftmark
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.01,0:26:36.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安家族领地与财产的合法继承人\N{\fs40}and all the lands and holdings of House Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.85,0:26:38.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你与戴蒙王子所生之子\N{\fs40}Your sons by Prince Daemon
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.85,0:26:41.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也将获得御前职务的殊荣\N{\fs40}will also be given places of high honor at court:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.85,0:26:44.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小伊耿将成为国王的侍从\N{\fs40}Aegon the Younger as the King's squire,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.39,0:26:46.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯将成为国王的侍酒\N{\fs40}Viserys as his cupbearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.40,0:26:48.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最后 国王出于仁慈\N{\fs40}Finally, the King, in his good grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.57,0:26:52.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,将赦免所有密谋反对他登基的骑士和领主\N{\fs40}will pardon any knight or lord who conspired against his ascent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.74,0:26:56.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我宁可把儿子们扔去喂龙\N{\fs40}I would rather feed my sons to the dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.49,0:27:03.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也不会让他们为你那篡位的酒鬼贱种国王执盾或者斟酒\N{\fs40}than have them carry shields and cups for your drunken, usurper cunt of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.91,0:27:07.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿·坦格利安坐在铁王座上\N{\fs40}Aegon Targaryen sits the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.38,0:27:10.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴征服者之冠\N{\fs40}He wears the Conqueror's crown,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.25,0:27:12.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,执征服者之剑\N{\fs40}wields the Conqueror's sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.09,0:27:13.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,冠征服者之名\N{\fs40}has the Conqueror's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.59,0:27:18.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他在万千民众的见证下由教会修士涂油加冕\N{\fs40}He was anointed by a septon of the Faith before the eyes of thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.43,0:27:22.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,集一切正统于一身\N{\fs40}Every symbol of legitimacy belongs to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.89,0:27:28.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有史塔克 徒利和拜拉席恩\N{\fs40}And then there is Stark, Tully, Baratheon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.27,0:27:32.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下对这些家族开出了优厚的条件\N{\fs40}Houses that have also received, and are at present,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.40,0:27:35.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,值得他们好好考虑一番\N{\fs40}considering generous terms from their king.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.24,0:27:41.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯陛下立我为继承人时\N{\fs40}Stark, Tully, and Baratheon all swore to me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.53,0:27:44.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,史塔克 徒利和拜拉席恩都曾向我宣誓效忠\N{\fs40}when King Viserys named me his heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.58,0:27:48.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,过时的誓言不会让你坐上铁王座 公主\N{\fs40}Stale oaths will not put you on the Iron Throne, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.42,0:27:53.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父亲生出儿子的那一天 继承顺位就改变了\N{\fs40}The succession changed the day your father sired a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.92,0:27:57.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只有你和他还在自欺欺人 我真是感到遗憾\N{\fs40}I only regret that you and he were the last to see the truth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.84,0:28:01.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不再是首相 伊耿也不是国王\N{\fs40}You are no more Hand than Aegon is king.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.22,0:28:02.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可恶的叛徒\N{\fs40}Fucking traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.61,0:28:16.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大学士\N{\fs40}Grand Maester.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.53,0:28:22.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\N{\fs40}What the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.26,0:28:42.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森太后并没有忘记你们曾经对彼此的爱\N{\fs40}Queen Alicent has not forgotten the love you once had for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.39,0:28:48.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无需流血牺牲 王国的和平将一如过去\N{\fs40}No blood need be spilled, so the realm can carry on in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.40,0:28:54.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王太后急切地盼望着你的回复\N{\fs40}Queen Alicent eagerly awaits your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.77,0:28:57.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她现在就可以得到回答 就用她父亲皱巴巴的鸡巴\N{\fs40}She can have her answer now, stuffed in her father's mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.11,0:28:58.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,塞在他自己的嘴里作为答复\N{\fs40}along with his withered cock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.36,0:29:00.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们结束这场闹剧吧\N{\fs40}Let's end this mummer's farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.87,0:29:05.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊利克爵士 把海塔尔大人押过来 我要亲自动手\N{\fs40}Ser Erryk, bring me Lord Hightower so I may take the pleasure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.17,0:29:11.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.97,0:29:25.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,明天 君临会收到我的答复\N{\fs40}King's Landing will have my answer on the morrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.62,0:29:51.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人类要当屠龙者难于登天\N{\fs40}It's no easy thing for a man to be a dragonslayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.66,0:29:54.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可龙杀得了龙 而且确实杀过\N{\fs40}But dragons can kill dragons. And have.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.63,0:29:58.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个简单的事实 我们比伊耿拥有更多龙\N{\fs40}The simple truth is this: we have more dragons than Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.05,0:30:01.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯经常谈起瓦雷利亚的历史\N{\fs40}Viserys spoke often of the Valyrian histories.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.47,0:30:03.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我再了解不过\N{\fs40}I know them well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.80,0:30:05.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当巨龙飞赴战场……\N{\fs40}When dragons flew to war...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.85,0:30:08.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一切陷入火海\N{\fs40}everything burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.43,0:30:13.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不想统治一个灰烬与白骨的王国\N{\fs40}I do not wish to rule over a kingdom of ash and bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.60,0:30:16.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在考虑海塔尔的条件吗 陛下？\N{\fs40}Are you considering the Hightowers' terms, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.94,0:30:20.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为女王 我对王国的真正责任是什么 巴提摩斯伯爵？\N{\fs40}As Queen, what is my true duty to the realm, Lord Bartimos?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.15,0:30:22.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确保和平与团结？\N{\fs40}Ensuring peace and unity?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.70,0:30:25.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是不计一切代价坐稳铁王座？\N{\fs40}Or that I sit the Iron Throne, no matter the cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.74,0:30:27.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是你父亲的说法\N{\fs40}That's your father talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.12,0:30:28.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我父亲死了\N{\fs40}My father's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.12,0:30:32.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而他选择我作为继承人\N{\fs40}And he chose me as his successor...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.71,0:30:37.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去守护王国 而不是让它一头冲入战争\N{\fs40}to defend the realm, not cast it headlong into war.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.34,0:30:38.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但敌人已经宣战\N{\fs40}Well, the enemy have declared war.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.59,0:30:41.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要怎么做？\N{\fs40}What are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.72,0:30:45.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所有人退下\N{\fs40}Clear the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.42,0:31:18.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,战争的可能性让你兴奋了吗\N{\fs40}Does the promise of war excite you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.08,0:31:19.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不能向海塔尔屈膝\N{\fs40}You cannot bend the knee to the Hightowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.96,0:31:21.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们窃取了你与生俱来的权利\N{\fs40}They stole your birthright.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.59,0:31:23.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果不必把奥托·海塔尔的头插在枪上\N{\fs40}If you could take the Iron Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.30,0:31:26.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就能拿下铁王座 你会这样做吗？\N{\fs40}without putting Otto Hightower's head on a spike, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.01,0:31:26.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不愤怒吗？\N{\fs40}Are you not angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.01,0:31:28.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为愤怒我就要宣战？\N{\fs40}I should declare war because I'm angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.89,0:31:29.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.43,0:31:31.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为镇压叛乱是你作为女王的职责\N{\fs40}Because it's your duty as Queen to crush rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.56,0:31:35.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你明白我的誓言应凌驾于个人野心之上\N{\fs40}You know my oath reaches beyond our personal ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.56,0:31:40.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,冰与火之歌\N{\fs40}A Song of Ice and Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.19,0:31:44.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs40}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.74,0:31:47.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,将来在北境 与黑暗的决战\N{\fs40}The coming war against the darkness in the North,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.49,0:31:49.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,征服者的梦\N{\fs40}The Conqueror's Dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.62,0:31:51.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是韦赛里斯指定我为继承人时告诉我的\N{\fs40}Viserys shared it with me when he named me heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.62,0:32:00.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我哥哥……是征兆和预言的奴隶\N{\fs40}My brother... was a slave to his omens and portents.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.88,0:32:05.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他软弱统治之时 总认为事出有因\N{\fs40}Anything to make his feckless reign appear to have purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.14,0:32:11.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们成王的不是梦\N{\fs40}Dreams didn't make us kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.18,0:32:13.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是龙\N{\fs40}Dragons did.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.66,0:32:33.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他从没告诉过你……\N{\fs40}He never told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是不是？\N{\fs40}did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.62,0:33:19.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要是哪个爷们当职时睡着了 肯定要挨我一顿鞭子\N{\fs40}I've had men whipped for falling asleep on their watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.00,0:33:27.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你不是爷们\N{\fs40}You are no man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.34,0:33:34.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你抛弃了我……\N{\fs40}You abandoned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.93,0:33:37.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在我最需要你的时候\N{\fs40}when I most needed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.85,0:33:41.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的两个孩子都被偷走了\N{\fs40}Both our children stolen from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.52,0:33:43.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当时我需要你\N{\fs40}I needed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.40,0:33:45.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,贝妮拉和雷妮娅需要你\N{\fs40}Baela and Rhaena needed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.90,0:33:48.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你却为了出海冒险而抛弃了我们\N{\fs40}and you abandoned us for more adventure at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.07,0:33:51.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恰如你一贯的风格\N{\fs40}As has always been your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.82,0:33:55.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我无处可去\N{\fs40}I had no other place to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.70,0:33:58.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我失去了一切\N{\fs40}I lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.04,0:34:00.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是我们 科利斯\N{\fs40}We lost, Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.96,0:34:02.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\fs40}We.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.93,0:34:18.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,据说我们有新国王了\N{\fs40}I understand we have a new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.39,0:34:21.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们家族被陌客投下了绵长的阴影\N{\fs40}The Stranger casts a long shadow over this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.19,0:34:29.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你弟弟也死了\N{\fs40}Your brother is also dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.03,0:34:37.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为他迫不及待想埋葬你 抢你的位子\N{\fs40}In his haste to bury you and claim your seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.08,0:34:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他在国王陛下面前\N{\fs40}he stood before the King
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.66,0:34:42.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当众宣称兰尼诺的孩子们是私生子\N{\fs40}and denounced Laenor's sons as illegitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.63,0:34:50.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙为此砍了他的脑袋\N{\fs40}Daemon took his head for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.80,0:34:59.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,肆无忌惮的野心素来是瓦列利安家的弱点\N{\fs40}Heedless ambition has always been a Velaryon weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.64,0:35:05.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是对的 雷妮丝\N{\fs40}You were right, Rhaenys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.40,0:35:10.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要的太多了 结果都是徒劳\N{\fs40}I reached too far. And for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.28,0:35:18.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们对铁王座的追求……结束了\N{\fs40}Our pursuit of the Iron Throne... is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.58,0:35:25.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们不会站到任何一边\N{\fs40}We shall declare for no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.00,0:35:29.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们就退守高潮城\N{\fs40}We will retire to High Tide
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.25,0:35:33.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,享受与孙辈的……天伦之乐 还有——\N{\fs40}to be content...with our grandchildren and--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.88,0:35:37.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰 小路和小乔都有权继承王座\N{\fs40}Jace, Luke, and Joff are claimants to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.76,0:35:41.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只要伊耿还是国王 男孩子们就有危险\N{\fs40}Those boys'll not be safe so long as Aegon is king.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.14,0:35:48.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,咱儿子的死 雷妮拉难脱干系\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra was complicit in our son's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.77,0:35:52.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那女孩儿将身边的一切摧毁殆尽\N{\fs40}That girl destroys everything she touches.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.48,0:35:54.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那"女孩儿"……\N{\fs40}That "girl"...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.53,0:35:56.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如今正将王国上下团结在一起\N{\fs40}is holding the realm together at present.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.78,0:35:59.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,围着地图桌的所有男人\N{\fs40}Every man standing 'round the Painted Table
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.66,0:36:01.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都在催促她把王国推入战争泥潭\N{\fs40}urges her to plunge the realm into war.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.20,0:36:07.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉是唯一表现出克制的人\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra's the only one who's demonstrated restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.50,0:36:10.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,战争的目的就是填满墓穴 亲爱的斯汤顿伯爵\N{\fs40}The purpose of war is to fill graveyards, my dear Lord Staunton.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.92,0:36:14.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,窍门在于怎么让敌方入土的人比我方多\N{\fs40}The trick is to put more of their men in the ground than your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.09,0:36:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你说得轻巧 只因你身为领主\N{\fs40}Easy words for a lord who commands
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.72,0:36:17.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可以安坐在城堡里发令\N{\fs40}from the safety of his castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.00,0:36:17.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这不会让这话反映的真相削减半分……\N{\fs40}Doesn't make it any less true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.43,0:36:19.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潮汛之主驾到！\N{\fs40}The Lord of the Tides!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.72,0:36:21.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯·瓦列利安伯爵……\N{\fs40}Lord Corlys Velaryon...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.60,0:36:26.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,及夫人 雷妮丝·坦格利安公主\N{\fs40}and his wife, the Princess Rhaenys Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.53,0:36:39.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸位大人\N{\fs40}My lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.20,0:36:40.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯伯爵\N{\fs40}Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.66,0:36:44.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看到您恢复健康 我们深感宽慰\N{\fs40}It brings much relief to see you hale and healthy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.79,0:36:49.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我为您的父亲致哀 公主\N{\fs40}I'm very sorry about your father, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.17,0:36:51.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他是个好人\N{\fs40}He was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.43,0:37:04.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙在哪儿\N{\fs40}Where is Daemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.77,0:37:08.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王子还有其他事务要处理\N{\fs40}There were other concerns which demanded the Prince's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.11,0:37:21.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些是已经公开效忠您的盟友？\N{\fs40}Your declared allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.07,0:37:26.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 要赢得铁王座 这远远不够\N{\fs40}- Yes. -Too few to win a war for the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.33,0:37:31.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,呃 我们还希望能够获得来自\N{\fs40}Well, we would also hope to have the support
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.08,0:37:34.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 艾林 拜拉席恩和史塔克家族的支持 - 希望\N{\fs40}- of Houses Arryn, Baratheon, and Stark. - Hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.96,0:37:36.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是傻瓜的盟友\N{\fs40}is the fool's ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.13,0:37:41.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,艾林和拜拉席恩家族与我们血脉相连\N{\fs40}Both Arryn and Baratheon share blood with my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.43,0:37:43.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且他们都曾对我宣誓效忠\N{\fs40}But all of them swore oaths to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.55,0:37:45.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我没记错的话\N{\fs40}As did House Hightower...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.47,0:37:46.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海塔尔家族也曾向你宣誓……\N{\fs40}if I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.72,0:37:49.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您也一样 科利斯伯爵\N{\fs40}As did you, Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.53,0:38:04.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您父亲的王国……\N{\fs40}Your father's realm...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.08,0:38:08.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是正义和荣誉之国\N{\fs40}was one of justice and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.04,0:38:14.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们两家因共同的血脉和事业联合在一起\N{\fs40}Our houses are bound by common blood and common cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.04,0:38:18.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海塔尔的叛国行径必将招致倾覆\N{\fs40}This Hightower treason cannot stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.68,0:38:28.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的家族和舰队都将全力支持您\N{\fs40}You have the full support of our fleet and house.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.85,0:38:31.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,女王陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.90,0:38:41.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不胜光荣 科利斯伯爵\N{\fs40}You honor me, Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.87,0:38:49.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝公主\N{\fs40}Princess Rhaenys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.91,0:38:57.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是 正如我对封臣们所说\N{\fs40}But, as I said to my bannermen
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.67,0:39:01.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我曾向父亲许诺 要维护王国的强大与团结\N{\fs40}I made a promise to my father to hold the realm strong and united.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.22,0:39:06.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就算战争无可避免 第一剑也不会由我挥出\N{\fs40}If war's first stroke is to fall, it will not be by my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.76,0:39:09.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您不准备采取行动？\N{\fs40}You do not mean to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.22,0:39:12.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谨慎而为不代表站着不动\N{\fs40}Taking caution does not mean standing fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.81,0:39:17.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,开战之前 我得先分清真正的盟友\N{\fs40}I wish to know who my allies are before I send them to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.53,0:39:30.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我在石阶列岛……拼死征战……\N{\fs40}The consequence of my...near-demise in the Stepstones...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.33,0:39:34.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,终于将其收入囊中\N{\fs40}is that we now control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.83,0:39:37.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这次我特意安排了重兵把守\N{\fs40}I took care to fully garrison the territory this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.50,0:39:41.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用不了几天 我的舰队便可完全封锁航道\N{\fs40}A total blockade of the shipping lanes will be in place in days, if not already.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.55,0:39:44.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,三城同盟会业已溃败\N{\fs40}The Triarchy have been routed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.05,0:39:46.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,狭海是我们的了\N{\fs40}The Narrow Sea is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.80,0:39:52.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我们进一步封锁喉道\N{\fs40}If we further seal the Gullet,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.68,0:39:55.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就能切断所有海上航行和贸易\N{\fs40}we can cut off all seaborne travel and trade
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.77,0:39:57.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,孤立君临\N{\fs40}to King's Landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.02,0:40:00.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会骑着梅丽亚斯亲自巡逻喉道\N{\fs40}I shall take Meleys and patrol the Gullet myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.74,0:40:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等我们围死狭海\N{\fs40}When we drain the Narrow Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.61,0:40:10.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就能包围君临\N{\fs40}we can surround King's Landing,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.70,0:40:12.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,围攻红堡\N{\fs40}lay siege to the Red Keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.04,0:40:15.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,逼绿党投降\N{\fs40}and force the Greens' surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.58,0:40:19.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要确保有足够人马包围君临\N{\fs40}If we are to have enough swords to surround King's Landing,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.38,0:40:23.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们就必须先得到临冬城 鹰巢城和风息堡的支持\N{\fs40}we must first secure the support of Winterfell, the Eyrie, and Storm's End.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.09,0:40:25.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我来准备渡鸦传书 陛下\N{\fs40}I'll prepare the ravens, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.97,0:40:28.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们去送信吧\N{\fs40}We should bear those messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.51,0:40:32.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙飞得比渡鸦快\N{\fs40}Dragons can fly faster than ravens
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.56,0:40:34.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙也更有说服力\N{\fs40}and they're more convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.73,0:40:38.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,派我们去吧\N{\fs40}Send us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.86,0:40:42.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王子说得对 陛下\N{\fs40}The Prince is right, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.95,0:40:52.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs40}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.95,0:40:56.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰卡里斯王子向北\N{\fs40}Prince Jacaerys will fly north.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.16,0:41:00.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,先去鹰巢城见我母亲的堂亲 简妮·艾林夫人\N{\fs40}First to the Eyrie to see my mother's cousin, the Lady Jeyne Arryn,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.42,0:41:03.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然后去临冬城 与克雷根·史塔克大人交涉\N{\fs40}and then to Winterfell to treat with Lord Cregan Stark
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.34,0:41:05.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,争取北境的支持\N{\fs40}for the support of the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.46,0:41:09.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,路斯里斯王子南下风息堡\N{\fs40}Prince Lucerys will fly south to Storm's End
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.34,0:41:12.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与博洛斯·拜拉席恩大人交涉\N{\fs40}and treat with Lord Borros Baratheon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.22,0:41:16.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们必须提醒这几位大人他们曾立下的誓言\N{\fs40}We must remind these lords of the oaths they swore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.98,0:41:20.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以及……背誓的代价\N{\fs40}And... the cost of breaking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.92,0:41:50.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都说坦格利安家族比凡人更接近神\N{\fs40}It's been said that as Targaryens, we are closer to gods than to men.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.18,0:41:55.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许铁王座也有一分功劳\N{\fs40}And the Iron Throne puts us a touch closer, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.89,0:42:00.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但如果我们要侍奉七大王国\N{\fs40}But, if we are to serve the Seven Kingdoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.85,0:42:03.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就必须接受他们的神明\N{\fs40}we must answer to their gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.86,0:42:09.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们要去 只能作为信使 而不是战士\N{\fs40}If you take this errand, you go as messengers... not as warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.03,0:42:12.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,切勿参与任何争斗\N{\fs40}You must take no part in any fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.82,0:42:17.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在 就七神的见证下向我发誓吧\N{\fs40}Swear it to me now under the eyes of the Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.87,0:42:24.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我发誓\N{\fs40}I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.92,0:42:30.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我发誓\N{\fs40}I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.34,0:42:32.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs40}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.01,0:42:40.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与我相比 克雷根·史塔克与你更加年龄相仿\N{\fs40}Cregan Stark is close to your age than is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.06,0:42:45.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望你们同为男人 能找到一些共同话题\N{\fs40}I would hope, that as men, you can find some common interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.94,0:42:47.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是 陛下\N{\fs40}Yes, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.70,0:42:57.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,风息堡离这不远\N{\fs40}Storm's End is a short flight from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.54,0:43:03.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,从你的祖母雷妮丝身上 你传承了拜拉席恩的血脉\N{\fs40}You have Baratheon blood from your grandmother, Rhaenys.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.29,0:43:04.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,此外……\N{\fs40}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.71,0:43:07.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,博洛斯大人素来骄傲\N{\fs40}Lord Borros is an eternally proud man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.09,0:43:12.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他会感到荣幸 能招待王国的王子\N{\fs40}He will be honored to host a prince of the realm...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.17,0:43:13.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和他的龙\N{\fs40}and his dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.52,0:43:25.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信你会受到热情款待\N{\fs40}I expect you will receive a very warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.10,0:43:28.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好的 母亲 陛——陛下\N{\fs40}Yes, Mother. Y-Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.37,0:43:40.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs40}Go to it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.30,0:47:23.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是路斯里斯·瓦列利安王子\N{\fs40}I am Prince Lucerys Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.05,0:47:26.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我给博洛斯大人带来了女王的信\N{\fs40}I bring a message to Lord Borros from the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.19,0:47:45.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,路斯里斯·瓦列利安王子到\N{\fs40}Prince Lucerys Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.70,0:47:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,此乃雷妮拉·坦格利安公主之子\N{\fs40}Son of Princess Rhaenyra Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.29,0:48:00.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,博洛斯大人\N{\fs40}Lord Borros...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.50,0:48:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我为您带来了我母亲……\N{\fs40}I brought you a message from my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.63,0:48:06.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,女王陛下的信\N{\fs40}the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.88,0:48:11.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可我今天才迎接过国王的使节\N{\fs40}Yet earlier this day, I received an envoy from the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.47,0:48:14.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,到底哪位是真的？\N{\fs40}Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.22,0:48:16.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王还是女王？\N{\fs40}King or Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.02,0:48:19.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙王家族好像弄不清楚谁来掌权啊 哈哈哈\N{\fs40}The House of the Dragon does not seem to know who rules it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.52,0:48:25.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你母亲的信呢？\N{\fs40}What's your mother's message?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.25,0:48:42.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,混蛋学士哪去了？\N{\fs40}Where's the bloody maester?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.79,0:49:20.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“提醒”我家父的誓言\N{\fs40}"Remind" me of my father's oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.88,0:49:24.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿国王至少还开出了条件\N{\fs40}King Aegon at least came with an offer:
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.92,0:49:27.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用联姻来换取我麾下的骑士和封臣\N{\fs40}my swords and banners for a marriage pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.01,0:49:31.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我照你母亲吩咐的做\N{\fs40}If I do as your mother bids...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.30,0:49:34.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你会娶我哪个女儿？\N{\fs40}which one of my daughters will you wed...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.35,0:49:37.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小子？\N{\fs40}boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.52,0:49:41.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大人……我无法联姻\N{\fs40}My lord... I am not free to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.02,0:49:44.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已有婚约\N{\fs40}I'm already betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.69,0:49:49.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以你空手就来了是吧\N{\fs40}So you come with empty hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.20,0:49:52.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,回家吧 小崽子\N{\fs40}Go home, pup.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.45,0:49:55.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,告诉你母亲 风息堡公爵不是她养的狗\N{\fs40}And tell your mother that the Lord of Storm's End
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.70,0:50:00.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用得着时吹吹哨子就能为她撕咬敌人\N{\fs40}is not some dog that she can whistle up at need to set against her foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.46,0:50:06.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会把您的答复转告给女王的 大人\N{\fs40}I shall take your answer to the Queen, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.55,0:50:14.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等等……\N{\fs40}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.93,0:50:17.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,斯壮大人\N{\fs40}my Lord Strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.39,0:50:26.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不会真的以为你在王国里随便飞一飞\N{\fs40}Did you really think that you could just fly about the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.82,0:50:29.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不费吹灰之力就能偷走我哥哥的王位吧？\N{\fs40}trying to steal my brother's throne at no cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.19,0:50:32.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会和你打架\N{\fs40}I will not fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.95,0:50:36.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是以信使的身份而来 不是战士\N{\fs40}I came as a messenger, not a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.91,0:50:38.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,打架有什么意思\N{\fs40}A fight would be little challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.62,0:50:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.71,0:50:45.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要你挖出一只眼睛\N{\fs40}I want you to put out your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.55,0:50:49.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,算是向我赔罪\N{\fs40}As payment for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.38,0:50:53.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一只就好\N{\fs40}One will serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.72,0:50:59.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会让你全瞎的\N{\fs40}I would not blind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.35,0:51:04.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嗯 我好送给母亲当作礼物\N{\fs40}Mm, plan to make a gift of it to my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.77,0:51:09.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.03,0:51:12.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不仅是个懦夫 还是个叛徒\N{\fs40}Then you are craven as well as a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.07,0:51:13.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,出去吵\N{\fs40}Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.60,0:51:15.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把你的眼珠子给我\N{\fs40}Give me your eye
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.70,0:51:17.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不然我就亲自动手了 野种！\N{\fs40}or I will take it, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.99,0:51:19.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别在我的大厅里动手！\N{\fs40}Not in my hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.91,0:51:22.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这孩子是作为使节来的\N{\fs40}The boy came as an envoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.79,0:51:24.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不允许在我的屋檐下流血\N{\fs40}I'll not have bloodshed beneath my roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.42,0:51:27.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,带路斯里斯王子去找他的龙\N{\fs40}Take Prince Lucerys back to his dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.67,0:51:29.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,马上\N{\fs40}Now.
