Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.47,0:52:06.52,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,注意！\N{\fs40}Dokimarvose!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.31,0:52:08.77,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,听我说 阿拉克斯！\N{\fs40}Laehossa ynot, Arrax!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.23,0:52:10.44,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,冷静！\N{\fs40}Lykirī!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.94,0:52:12.08,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,听着！\N{\fs40}Ryptēs!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.08,0:52:13.36,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,听话！\N{\fs40}Rȳbās!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.19,0:52:20.49,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,飞 阿拉克斯！\N{\fs40}Sōvēs, Arrax!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.00,0:53:50.75,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,傻瓜！瓦格哈尔！\N{\fs40}Mittys! Vagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.92,0:54:00.38,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,快！转弯！\N{\fs40}Aderī! Pālēs!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.86,0:54:55.65,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,你欠了债\N{\fs40}Jemēla gēlȳni enkā!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.90,0:54:58.19,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,小子！\N{\fs40}Taobus!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.70,0:55:04.53,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,不 阿拉克斯\N{\fs40}Daor, Arrax!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.49,0:55:08.04,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,听话 阿拉克斯！往上飞！\N{\fs40}Dohaerās, Arrax! Hepās, vēzot!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.47,0:55:12.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不 不！不 瓦格哈尔！不！\N{\fs40}No, no, no, no, no! No, Vhagar! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.81,0:55:13.69,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,不!\N{\fs40}Daor!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.69,0:55:15.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,听话 瓦格哈尔 不！\N{\fs40}Serve me, Vhagar! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.32,0:55:17.11,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,听话 瓦格哈尔！\N{\fs40}Dohaerās, Vhagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.48,0:55:41.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦格哈尔！不！不！\N{\fs40}Vhagar! No! No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:35.20,Note_top,,0,0,0,,后排右一教士胸前的高等瓦雷利亚文字意为“教士”。
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.77,0:44:44.53,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,吞吐火焰 驾驭双翼\N{\fs40}Drakari pykiros, Tīkummo jemiros.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.37,0:44:56.88,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,双头并立 向三而歌\N{\fs40}Yn lantyz bartossa, Saelot vāedis.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.50,0:45:06.26,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,由我之声 烈火言语\N{\fs40}Hen ñuhā elēnī: Perzyssy vestretis,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.66,0:45:17.75,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,血之魔法 牺牲已偿\N{\fs40}Se gēlȳn irūdaks, Ānogrose.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.75,0:45:28.66,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,火之言辞 辅以明眸\N{\fs40}Perzyro udrȳssi, Ezīmptos laehossi.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.83,0:45:38.01,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,三者合一 吾向汝歌\N{\fs40}Hārossa letagon, Aōt vāedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.13,0:45:59.02,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,龙之三头 齐聚合一\N{\fs40}Hae mērot gierūli: Se hāros bartossi,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.40,0:46:12.00,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,命定翱翔 自由美丽\N{\fs40}Prūmȳsa sōvīli, Gevī dāerī.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.01,0:28:34.51,Note_rotation_Left - 22,,0,0,0,,{\frz353.1\pos(1517.333,884.333)}娜梅莉亚的舰队\N虽然用缆索\N捆在一起，\N但还是在\N第一次\N风暴来袭时\N被冲散到\N海上四处：\N东方、\N西方，\N乃至向南\N到了\N海盗肆虐的\N蛇蜥群岛。
